General.Name: ScandiDos AB
General.Description: ScandiDos AB (publ) provides measurement systems and software designed for the QA and validation requirements of the new treatments implemented in clinics worldwide. The company offers Delta4 Discover and Delta4 Phantom+ for the QA of advanced radiation therapy procedures such as VMAT, RapidArc, IMRT, and Tomotherapy. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Uppsala, Sweden.
